## Deployment Steps

### Local Development
1. `npm install`
2. `npm run dev`
3. Open http://localhost:5173

### Production Build
1. `npm run build`
2. Deploy `dist` folder to hosting provider

### Firebase Hosting
1. `npm run build`
2. `firebase deploy`

